-- GE in talks to sell appliances business - Bloomberg
-- By Sagarika Jaisinghani in Bangalore
-- Wed Jul 16, 2014 02:14PM EDT
-- None



July 16 (Reuters) - General Electric Co <GE.N> is in talks with potential suitors about selling its household appliances business, Bloomberg reported, citing people familiar with the matter.

The business may fetch $1.5 billion to $2.5 billion in a sale, Bloomberg said. (http://bloom.bg/1oYC38h)